                     <rubric>Veritas theologie secundum Thomam de Alquino doctorem</rubric>
                     <incipit type="prol.">Veritatis theologice sublimitas</incipit>
                     <incipit type="text">Deum esse multis</incipit>
                     <note>According to the list of chapters which precedes this text, the title of the work is 'Veritas theologie secundum Thomam de Alquino [Aquino] doctorem'
